04:34.404 --> 04:36.972
-To ask him.
-To ask him if he knows
about Memo 618?

04:37.015 --> 04:38.190
Yes.

04:38.234 --> 04:39.888
Is that smart?

04:39.931 --> 04:41.933
I don't know anymore.

04:48.723 --> 04:51.682
Hi. I need to speak
to Bryan Kneef.

04:51.726 --> 04:53.902
This way, Ms. Lockhart.

04:53.945 --> 04:56.078
-[seabirds chirping]
-They're waiting for you.

04:56.121 --> 04:58.994
