05:11.093 --> 05:12.312
GAVIN:
Diane.

05:12.355 --> 05:14.531
Thank you for coming.

05:14.575 --> 05:16.620
You're welcome.
Uh, was I expected?

05:16.664 --> 05:18.622
Yes. Of course.

05:18.666 --> 05:21.538
Uh, you know what? I don't thinkyou've met, uh, Tom,

05:21.582 --> 05:24.367
Danny, Jim, Roger,

05:24.411 --> 05:27.370
Susan, Linda, Big Tom,

05:27.414 --> 05:30.634
Dana, Nate and Dhruhmil.

05:30.678 --> 05:33.942
Oh, and Bryan Kneef.I think you two know each other.

05:33.985 --> 05:35.944
No. We haven't met.

05:35.987 --> 05:38.425
-Just online. Diane.
-[Roger hiccups]

