my clients.

06:47.058 --> 06:48.799
DIANE:
No. That is a lie.

06:48.843 --> 06:52.150
You blocked me when I asked
about Memo 618.

06:52.194 --> 06:54.022
-GAVIN: What is that?
-DIANE: I don't know.

06:54.065 --> 06:56.720
But I've had
two pro bono cases disappear

06:56.764 --> 06:58.983
when the judge
was given Memo 618.

06:59.027 --> 07:00.855
-It has nothing to do with me.
-DIANE: No.

07:00.898 --> 07:02.770
GAVIN: Okay, here's whatI suggest. Diane, you won't dig

07:02.813 --> 07:05.729
into Bryan's clients.
Bryan, you won't block

07:05.773 --> 07:08.123
Diane's Internet access.
Understood?

07:08.166 --> 07:09.733
Uh, yes.

07:09.777 --> 07:12.780
