07:26.663 --> 07:28.839
Kneef had one case with
two years of billable hours,

07:28.883 --> 07:31.276
-but no docket number.
-What?

07:33.670 --> 07:35.629
-A case that disappeared?
-Yes.

07:35.672 --> 07:38.675
