when it disappeared.

07:38.719 --> 07:40.677
-I don't see a client.
-No, it's not in the records.

07:40.721 --> 07:42.636
But...

07:42.679 --> 07:45.900
it lists the associate
on the case.

07:45.943 --> 07:47.205
[keyboard clicking]

07:57.128 --> 07:59.696
-Yes, ma'am?
-You're not shaving anymore.

07:59.740 --> 08:03.178
I got a special dispensation.

08:03.221 --> 08:05.267
