to review the legal citing

09:17.295 --> 09:18.775
and he never returned.

09:20.385 --> 09:23.127
Uh-- He never returned
from the recess?

09:23.171 --> 09:24.868
Correct.

09:24.912 --> 09:27.479
-And no one followed up?
-Well, we didn't.

09:27.523 --> 09:29.177
We were losing,
so it was a gift.

09:29.220 --> 09:31.788
[laughs]: I don't know why the
plaintiffs never followed up.

09:31.832 --> 09:35.270
Was there ever a mention
of a Memo 618?

09:35.313 --> 09:36.924
No. What's that?

09:36.967 --> 09:39.753
Uh, we're not sure.

09:39.796 --> 09:42.799
What was the citing that
the judge wanted to review?

09:42.843 --> 09:45.628
57 U.S.C. 3335.

09:45.672 --> 09:48.109
Kneef had argued it meant
the case was moot.

09:48.152 --> 09:49.632
U.S. Code...?

09:49.676 --> 09:52.069
3335.

10:19.531 --> 10:22.186
