10:55.002 --> 10:56.264
Oh. Yeah, when they remodeled,

10:56.307 --> 10:58.092
it made it easier
to move the books.

10:58.135 --> 11:01.095
Why have law books
if we can't use them?

11:01.138 --> 11:03.097
For looks?

11:03.140 --> 11:05.273
Well, if you need something,
just check online.

11:08.232 --> 11:09.451
[sighs]

11:16.110 --> 11:17.546
This case you were on.

11:17.589 --> 11:19.417
-Who was the plaintiff?
-Uh, hold on.

11:19.461 --> 11:21.681
Um, the wife of the prisoner...

11:21.724 --> 11:23.726
