11:38.872 --> 11:42.919
So, what happened
with this prison ban lawsuit?

11:42.963 --> 11:45.313
Well, I represented
Nola Garnett.

11:45.356 --> 11:47.097
Above and beyond.

11:47.141 --> 11:49.099
Never missed a filing deadline.

11:49.143 --> 11:52.102
