using alliteration

11:52.146 --> 11:54.104
that I wrote out on index cards.

11:54.148 --> 11:57.107
Hmm. But the case
was just dropped?

11:57.151 --> 11:58.413
GABE:
Mmm.

11:58.456 --> 12:00.023
Through no fault of mine.

12:00.067 --> 12:02.156
And now she is suing me.

12:02.199 --> 12:04.767
-Uh, who is?
-Nola Garnett.

12:04.811 --> 12:07.596
For ineffective assistance.

12:07.639 --> 12:09.598
Me.

12:09.641 --> 12:10.947
Ineffective.

12:10.991 --> 12:12.775
-[chuckles] Can you imagine?
-I can't.

12:12.819 --> 12:14.908
-Because this case
was just dropped?
-GABE: Mmm.

12:14.951 --> 12:16.953
They never gave me
any kind of explanation.

12:16.997 --> 12:18.781
Did the defense attorney

12:18.825 --> 12:21.915
cite a law-- U.S. 3335?

12:21.958 --> 12:23.917
Maybe. I don't know.

12:23.960 --> 12:27.485
But now, in additionto all the rest of my caseload,

12:27.529 --> 12:29.139
