12:52.684 --> 12:56.036
with these type of suits?

12:57.341 --> 13:00.910
Some. Yes.

13:00.954 --> 13:02.912
CHARLOTTE:
Thank you.

13:02.956 --> 13:05.915
-Hey.
-Hey.

13:05.959 --> 13:08.526
-Mmm.
