was dismissed,

23:03.338 --> 23:05.775
what steps did you take
to challenge the dismissal?

23:05.819 --> 23:07.429
What steps?

23:07.473 --> 23:08.430
Yes.

23:08.474 --> 23:10.737
Well...

23:10.780 --> 23:13.087
I got... angry.

23:13.130 --> 23:14.088
MONICA:
Good.

23:14.131 --> 23:15.437
And?

23:15.481 --> 23:19.441
And I wrote a very, very,

23:19.485 --> 23:22.183
very detailed letter
to the judge.

23:22.226 --> 23:23.619
