23:23.663 --> 23:25.665
-Nope.
-Mm.

23:26.666 --> 23:28.755
Did you send it?

23:30.974 --> 23:32.802
Well, no,

23:32.846 --> 23:34.456
but that wasn't my fault.

23:34.500 --> 23:36.371
The mail delivery in my office

23:36.415 --> 23:38.547
has been a disaster.

23:38.591 --> 23:42.203
Do you know that song by Bob
Dylan, "Everything is Broken"?

23:42.246 --> 23:43.813
It's so true.

23:43.857 --> 23:46.337
Mm-hmm. And did you appeal
the judge's ruling?

23:46.381 --> 23:48.470
No, but that wasn't my fault,
either.

23:48.514 --> 23:49.993
There was nothing to appeal.

23:50.037 --> 23:51.604
The judge never ruled.

23:51.647 --> 23:53.954
He just...
counted on me forgetting.

23:53.997 --> 23:55.825
And did you forget it?

23:55.869 --> 23:57.479
No, I thought
the judge was gonna call

23:57.523 --> 23:59.002
the court back into session.

23:59.046 --> 24:01.004
-But he didn't.
-DIANE: Did you think

24:01.048 --> 24:02.745
