attorney, Bryan Kneef,

24:35.299 --> 24:37.519
and...
get some more background.

24:37.563 --> 24:39.042
Yeah.

24:39.086 --> 24:40.783
Wasn't my fault.

24:40.827 --> 24:42.219
-It was his fault.
-Mm.

24:42.263 --> 24:43.220
Call him.

24:43.264 --> 24:44.483
Ah.

24:44.526 --> 24:45.788
This must be important.

24:45.832 --> 24:47.877
We're in
the big conference room.

24:47.921 --> 24:49.270
That's new.

24:50.576 --> 24:52.621
Will your attorney
be joining us, Mr. North?

24:52.665 --> 24:53.883
Jenkins.

24:53.927 --> 24:56.103
I thought that was a pen name.

24:56.146 --> 24:58.061
Jumaane Alan Jenkins
is my birth name.

24:58.105 --> 24:59.889
I went by "Alan North"
when I worked here

24:59.933 --> 25:01.238
because I know how you

25:01.282 --> 25:03.240
all value the bourgeois
signifiers of whiteness.

25:03.284 --> 25:04.503
[chuckles]

25:04.546 --> 25:05.504
Dear God.

25:05.547 --> 25:06.635
To your question, Liz,

25:06.679 --> 25:07.854
I'm appearing pro se.

25:07.897 --> 25:09.420
Okay, then.

25:09.464 --> 25:11.422
Mr. Jenkins,

25:11.466 --> 25:13.860
last night,
you told the audience

25:13.903 --> 25:15.862
during a talkback Q&A

25:15.905 --> 25:19.039
