25:21.911 --> 25:22.869
Um...
[clears throat]

25:22.912 --> 25:24.740
"This play is based

25:24.784 --> 25:26.263
"on real people, not types.

25:26.307 --> 25:28.744
"Uh, like the divorcing
white guy.

25:28.788 --> 25:30.398
